  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>카탈로그 디자인에 진심인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-398602db-9cd7-4827-9163-c26527bcb791\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899936767/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bbc5a492-037a-49ff-8371-d5f6734645e0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-36023694-4411-433c-b722-234e4ce4e08a\" style=\"\">소소상점 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">좋은 디자인이 나오기 위해서는...</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">어떤 품목의 디자인이든 소통이 가장 중요합니다. 카탈로그 역시 고객과의 소통이 가장 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0f608761-7c2b-461e-acf6-5dcdfdbb9347\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d6b9bd8a-b5b9-48a1-89a2-8613698a5749\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c0751405-b84e-4de6-9d64-81757bc0dca6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5aa6d1cd-c0dc-4022-8f37-15a4dffb17fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객님이 요구하는 컨셉이 무엇인지를 파악하는 것이 가장 필요합니다. 컨셉은 고객님이 정할 수 있고 저희와 상담을 통해 정할 수도 있습니다. 다만 상황에 따라 기획비가 추가될 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aec9cd16-3edd-4fd4-bb64-d60fd0fe981b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-006d499a-8189-44d7-b8f4-95c7aaa20acf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-51349fc7-cd77-46f2-9df7-d79143429285\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-250ed356-c86d-4e7f-aa14-962177ec874e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-074a0b21-9626-43a5-8056-38a3e97fd259\" style=\"color:#000000;\">좋은 디자이너란</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7d6c6a6a-1dbf-4104-b074-ff8b2903f24a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-94f88efd-faf3-421f-ac98-f6318116eaea\" style=\"color:#000000;\">고객의 니즈(Needs)를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-79afb708-7e61-4f26-b4ff-8138ee20eaf6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-838c3b1a-cc98-4260-8f97-8cf81c479ce9\" style=\"color:#000000;\">가장 잘 파악하는 사람입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-36e7f6ff-561d-4fd9-9c50-c3c19be9967c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e8e3e2b-2675-4cab-9f4f-4a404d64be85\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f027b9b4-52fb-4dfa-aed5-b539f95d86fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3064dff3-8066-4514-ba9a-ec9d95664d51\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d1e7666-3baf-46e8-8e50-cb6478a8b8c8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 다음 사항을 약속드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-388d03ac-2af6-4b0e-b99b-0020e4dd96d6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d607a31d-411d-4b68-93a7-0940a698ec55\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e1d711f-d1a9-49d4-b09d-53664f8e7667\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-898d9d29-44ec-48f7-94a4-b3e13c54dc67\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>될 때까지 합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d290a458-ebfe-44c5-8e1e-9a562c2f6d3c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eb23d681-e7cb-4854-930f-f7432a8f9b26\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인은 될 때까지 하겠습니다. 이 말은 고객이 만족할 때까지 란 의미입니다. 이 의미는 매우 어려운 작업입니다. 고객이 계속적인 수정을 요구하면 계속 수정해야 하는 것은 숙명이지만 이것은 시간과 비용이 드는 일입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7f0a5bb2-3f0f-4f9b-9362-924a92c8f974\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3904c30e-2d2b-4ded-b03e-6c090d51a6c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-abbd49e5-8cfc-494a-8ef6-8a49129dd224\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cf59ea9d-7a39-4140-ae32-3ed5a916b569\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 고객과의 소통을 통해 이 비용을 명확하게 협의하여 요청드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-988c0139-4c4f-4c91-a802-d2c4bbf0f99c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dbc43932-abc3-4620-bdcf-fef6670b6bea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6a950dc9-105e-4e70-a5aa-c6d99cd9d33e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9305067b-5111-415d-aa31-a46f4fb7a1de\" style=\"color:#555555;\">1회 수정 비용 등을 명확하게 요청드리고 서로가 협의된 시점까지는 그 비용을 감안하여 견적하겠습니다. 몇 번의 수정이든 고객이 만족할 때까지 진행하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-58ce8d29-68e7-41d6-a708-3f14c30bab02\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-21129213-cf54-47e9-a41e-997eaca1c9e9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5283a007-0369-4321-9f11-112930d75c89\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-219f3122-f722-4711-acf5-09d4b5607026\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 디자인이라는 것은 무척 주관적입니다. 그렇기 때문에 (주)파파스컴퍼니의 디자인이 100% 마음에 든다는 보장은 없습니다. 그렇기 때문에 디자인 시안이 마음에 들지 않는다면 디자인 선입금의 30% 정도만을 청구하고 드롭하겠습니다. 저희와 맞지 않는 고객님을 손해를 보게 하면서 끌고 가지는 않겠다는 말입니다. 빠르게 협의하여 드롭하고 고객님도 맞는 디자인 회사를 찾을 수 일도록 도와드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3a35eb18-0e1e-4a1f-aaa7-bb45112aa43d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f3ab662b-e052-424d-9ca8-838bb43c58f6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f0e1325b-20b2-45d9-ad2e-238f1815a86c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b52b1a1c-ec24-4346-8edb-0342025c6731\" style=\"color:#555555;\">드롭 부분은 참 어려운 숙제이자 정말 큰 결정입니다. 물론 쌍방의 노력에 의해 최대한의 접점을 찾겠지만 이것이 불가능할 때 저희는 빠르게 드롭하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a3b515c8-6399-499e-8252-db9f4f87abe9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899936767/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-16a897d7-c1d0-492d-934b-e3659b82e3f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899936767/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dd93edee-f562-402c-a071-ab9cecdb401a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-59228abb-77dc-4496-a969-791666d1e0f6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7c87920e-3f13-4c84-8f4c-93ab23d9c4b3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#bdfbfa;\">합리적인 디자인 비용을 청구하고 저희와 맞지 않는다고 판단되시면 빠르게 드롭하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-62ad5bf6-df8d-466b-adc1-f282cbcaf77e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a14529b1-73d9-4e2e-b117-64a13cccc551\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-25347442-c8da-4465-bdc1-b746ea52faa4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b1160f1a-b11f-4836-bac3-9eb41e484b28\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>가장 빠르게 합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c2496e6-0790-473e-bc65-f47e9177cc3b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dea4cdb6-81b6-4752-8328-b9f13dea1869\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인은 빠르게 진행한다고 좋은 퀄리티가 나오는 것은 아닙니다. 그렇다고 한 달씩(?) 디자인한다고 최고의 디자인 퀄리티가 나오는 것도 아닙니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4689ccf5-32bb-46bb-9d12-73e7688a7ab0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-674e372b-7fd0-4436-bf56-5782abf356f0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니이 약속하는 것은 디자인 견적을 가장 빠르게 드릴 수 있다는 겁니다. 견적이 컨펌되면 다시 가장 빠르게 시안과 컨셉을 위한 소통을 준비하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f8ac37f-f837-419e-90c9-d47a60181a3a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b983d81c-fb97-41eb-97e3-c93c35fd3eae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b193a272-5364-4a7b-92a6-2a734a749035\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-22608522-275c-4d2a-a4a2-3f8fe95aa8ec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주문과 견적, 시안 제출 동안의 시간을 최대한 절약하겠다고 약속드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-12833414-e0c3-4a76-ae14-2b6e847a81f5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899936767/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-00bfa440-3279-494c-93af-da0169fde4d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899936767/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b2f84f1c-c2e5-4894-b6a3-867f7b6df839\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-af966336-507a-40db-b1b6-7e3676402003\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e0e30f71-2a10-4148-a5e3-42f3472560b1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#bdfbfa;\">견적과 소통까지 결정되는 시간을 가장 빠르게 당겨서 만 24시간이 넘지 않도록 하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-17729c61-1904-481d-a5ab-d7b0d9fdced6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1cea2849-51c1-4acf-ae4c-0b83f22d4a2c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c4070a0c-ff89-49c5-8258-f1c6bc2e6405\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-af97b250-0e66-4dd0-8d94-bd1c9d4ce5d7\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>인쇄까지 주문하시면 할인하여 드립니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0a40e854-0b22-4428-881a-00cfb88baee9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e4a9f41f-eb49-4add-8f35-8666129066bd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인과 인쇄까지 주문해 주시면 할인금액으로 제안 드립니다. 기본 가격을 제안 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-17194586-9f6b-4fe6-bb52-dbdddea2aed4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-845fce0b-a825-48b4-a391-21c6871f1110\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8e1621b2-72a6-4e03-b2db-e01b239ae769\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-df2accb6-4d97-4f1a-b511-2029414370aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>20페이지 이내 디자인 비용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9b419537-8ad2-49e7-8009-3c29dfce403b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e35f083d-f85d-4015-9bb0-b0e31a63bc21\" style=\"color:#555555;\">페이지당 10만 원 ~ 15만 원 내외</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-66276cc3-29c4-4794-91b2-be0e5db2d513\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-514171fd-abee-4bbf-b562-d1c0a044d493\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4cb1d91c-9397-48d4-9ae8-c243c713a413\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6b8e2223-02ce-44f0-bea8-1745e2ff8b1c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>20페이지 ~ 50페이지 이내 디자인 비용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-323db6c5-3797-4412-981b-c262089b499c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-17ce00d3-aa70-4656-918a-7a9516ca7f2e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">페이지당 5만 원 ~ 8만 원 내외</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-66c93a49-2be0-4687-b6fe-31fe5d735300\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-73f7f68e-ee75-4ca2-8495-a0d1492f7dae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9c4f121a-9ccd-459d-8a95-34936ee67d21\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d0b543e5-bb8f-4567-b896-968a6a8d0750\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>50페이지 이상 디자인 비용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ef8af26-39aa-419c-be4f-92561262b8a8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-49655146-bdc2-4b09-96fc-65d522cfe150\" style=\"color:#555555;\">페이지당 5만 원 내외</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c276fa9-9821-45d8-a385-00db11dd4ac7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e64ff5cf-828f-4cdd-b62c-5b3af1c5982f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5cb4f0c-62e8-4dd3-ab26-68fa9045f186\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-eb6d7005-4c4a-4937-aa31-b45d34e6a6c6\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>추가 금액이 발생되는 경우</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-79a8032a-b4a9-47ea-b007-2daeaeebdb8a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4e3e2e0f-acdf-474a-b4b6-182dae9f1cec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">특별한 상업용 이미지를 원할 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c9e2cb04-cf82-4fd2-8e46-d51dfc0eb2bf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b9493142-5f2a-47e5-8ea4-fc1cd19fd715\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품 촬영이나 이미지 목업 작업이 필요한 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-da44e208-ddfc-4e7b-922a-4b6590ab9718\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-faff8a76-1b6d-4fc3-aca5-09113ff6fe0e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">특별한 기획이나 컨셉이 요구되는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f4422357-dc27-471c-8938-3ccc7502a997\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223899936767/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-1ec156c0-e37a-4bd1-94f9-2e43118e51c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-52b23e08-7628-4656-ae0d-096cc4314b6c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-195668cd-2749-4a4f-90d3-dfad2e76bff8\" style=\"\">결론</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-803f285a-029d-4a9b-8f3c-bcde608641f8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-047974f7-08b7-4f67-bc55-a5d10642db7c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7612b473-7a68-46fa-afc9-0f2b9d775257\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 디자인 회사와의 소통 때문에 애먹어본 경험이 있으신 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-74e5a6ce-e81b-414b-b18d-c7879fbd0f03\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ecffd3f8-f909-4ffa-9e3e-c3b5b2a1b64a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 마음에 들지 않는데 선결제 때문에 작업을 이어온 회사</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-17039c60-9e45-47b7-8f32-6c5588cf923d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6ee051ca-956e-4b59-ac4b-a7e622e26f65\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 비용에 대한 상담 시 협의가 안된 고객</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}